<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 09:14:37 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>香港活动人士擅自携带投诉表格出狱被定罪</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/hong-kong-activist-convicted-taking-complaint-form-out-prison-without-2024-07-29/</link><description>香港一家法院周一判定活动人士周文豪及其律师吴菲丽丝有罪，罪名是涉嫌去年五月未经授权向监察员携带投诉表格出狱。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 08:09:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/hong-kong-activist-convicted-taking-complaint-form-out-prison-without-2024-07-29/</guid></item><item><title>中国谴责美日在海上问题和军事扩张问题上的“不实指控”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-rebukes-us-japan-false-accusations-maritime-issues-military-expansion-2024-07-29/</link><description>中国外交部周一表示，美国和日本之间的联合声明在海上问题上“错误地指责”中国，并指责中国正常的军事发展和国防政策。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 07:47:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-rebukes-us-japan-false-accusations-maritime-issues-military-expansion-2024-07-29/</guid></item><item><title>路透调查显示中国7月份制造业活动继续下滑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-manufacturing-activity-seen-extending-decline-july-2024-07-29/</link><description>路透周一的一项民意调查显示，中国7月份工厂活动可能连续第三个月萎缩，由于旷日持久的房地产危机和就业不稳定拖累经济增长，官员们需要推出进一步刺激措施的预期依然存在。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 07:02:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-manufacturing-activity-seen-extending-decline-july-2024-07-29/</guid></item><item><title>路透调查显示，台湾第二季度经济增长放缓，但受到人工智能热潮的支撑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/taiwan-q2-economic-growth-seen-slowing-supported-by-ai-boom-2024-07-29/</link><description>路透社周一的一项民意调查显示，尽管人工智能技术的高需求推动了出口强劲，但依赖贸易的台湾第二季度经济增长可能放缓。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 05:31:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/taiwan-q2-economic-growth-seen-slowing-supported-by-ai-boom-2024-07-29/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：亚洲因鸽派利率希望而反弹</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-view-europe-2024-07-29/</link><description>韦恩·科尔 (Wayne Cole) 对欧洲和全球市场未来一天的展望。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 04:40:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-view-europe-2024-07-29/</guid></item><item><title>四国外长谴责危险的南海行动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/quad-foreign-ministers-meet-tokyo-talks-maritime-security-cyber-2024-07-29/</link><description>澳大利亚、印度、日本和美国外长周一表示，他们对南中国海的恐吓和危险行为感到严重关切，并承诺加强该地区的海上安全。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 02:18:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/quad-foreign-ministers-meet-tokyo-talks-maritime-security-cyber-2024-07-29/</guid></item><item><title>法院称碧桂园清算听证会推迟至明年一月</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/country-garden-liquidation-hearing-adjourned-january-next-year-court-says-2024-07-29/</link><description>香港一家法院周一将寻求碧桂园清算请愿书的听证会推迟至 2025 年 1 月 20 日，这让这家陷入困境的中国开发商有了喘息的机会，该开发商正试图敲定离岸债务重组计划。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 02:16:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/country-garden-liquidation-hearing-adjourned-january-next-year-court-says-2024-07-29/</guid></item><item><title>债权人寻求破产程序后，中国恒大的电动汽车部门下线</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/shares-china-evergrande-new-energy-vehicle-set-open-up-9-2024-07-29/</link><description>周一早盘，中国恒大新能源汽车股价下跌 7%，此前该公司旗下两家子公司的个人债权人寻求法院批准这些子公司进入破产程序并进行重组。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 01:41:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/shares-china-evergrande-new-energy-vehicle-set-open-up-9-2024-07-29/</guid></item><item><title>朝中社称，朝鲜金正恩视察中国边境附近的洪水地区</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-koreas-kim-jong-un-inspects-flooded-areas-near-china-border-kcna-says-2024-07-28/</link><description>金正恩指责官员们对危机应对措施的准备不足。</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 22:45:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-koreas-kim-jong-un-inspects-flooded-areas-near-china-border-kcna-says-2024-07-28/</guid></item><item><title>梅洛尼誓言“重启”意大利与中国的合作</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/italys-meloni-vows-relaunch-cooperation-with-china-ansa-2024-07-28/</link><description>意大利总理乔治亚·梅洛尼周日誓言要“重启”与中国的合作，并在上任以来首次正式访问北京期间签署了一项三年行动计划。</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 10:44:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/italys-meloni-vows-relaunch-cooperation-with-china-ansa-2024-07-28/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾称中国曲解南海协议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-china-mischaracterised-south-china-sea-resupply-mission-deal-2024-07-28/</link><description>一名中国官员表示，中国海警在执行任务前接到通知，并在“现场确认”后放行了一艘船只。</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 08:29:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-china-mischaracterised-south-china-sea-resupply-mission-deal-2024-07-28/</guid></item><item><title>美国升级驻日军事指挥权，警告中国威胁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/us-announce-military-command-revamp-japan-official-says-2024-07-28/</link><description>美国周日宣布计划对其驻日军事指挥部进行重大调整，以加深与其盟友部队的协调，两国将中国视为该地区面临的“最大战略挑战”。</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 03:15:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/us-announce-military-command-revamp-japan-official-says-2024-07-28/</guid></item><item><title>朝鲜在朝鲜战争周年纪念日发誓“彻底消灭”敌人</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-korea-vows-total-destruction-enemy-korean-war-anniversary-2024-07-28/</link><description>据官方媒体朝中社周日报道，朝鲜领导人金正恩下令，誓言一旦发生战争，将“彻底摧毁”敌人。</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 00:36:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-korea-vows-total-destruction-enemy-korean-war-anniversary-2024-07-28/</guid></item><item><title>中国电动汽车电池制造商CATL第二季度利润增长更快</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinese-ev-battery-maker-catl-posts-134-jump-second-quarter-profit-2024-07-26/</link><description>中国电动汽车电池巨头宁德时代第二季度利润增长更快，尽管全球最大汽车市场的电动汽车需求放缓，而地缘政治紧张局势给其海外扩张蒙上了阴影。</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 11:53:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinese-ev-battery-maker-catl-posts-134-jump-second-quarter-profit-2024-07-26/</guid></item><item><title>投资者表示，税收漏洞的终结可能会削弱 Shein 的 IPO 吸引力</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/end-tax-loophole-risks-dimming-sheins-ipo-appeal-investors-say-2024-07-26/</link><description>关注该行业的投资者表示，欧盟和其他地区当局终止低价值包裹税收减免的举措威胁到了 Shein 的盈利能力，并有可能削弱这家快时尚零售商在计划上市之前的长期吸引力。</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 08:14:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/end-tax-loophole-risks-dimming-sheins-ipo-appeal-investors-say-2024-07-26/</guid></item></channel></rss>